# Docker Build Context Ignore List
# Optimizes docker build time and prevents unwanted files from being sent to Docker daemon

# Build outputs
**/bin/
**/obj/
**/out/
**/artifacts/
**/nupkg/

# IDE & Editor files
**/.vs/
**/.vscode/
**/.idea/
*.user
*.suo
*.userosscache
*.sln.docstates

# Version Control
**/.git/
**/.gitignore
**/.gitattributes
**/.dockerignore

# Aspire & Local Dev Tools
**/.aspire/
**/.devcontainer/

# Secrets & Local Environments
**/.env
**/.env.local
**/.env.*.local
!**/.env.example

# Documentation, Plans, & Media
**/README.md
**/LICENSE
**/plan/
**/*.md
**/*.png
**/*.jpg

# Tests & Workflows
**/.github/
**/tests/
